This paper focuses on software engineering (SE) and programming languages (PL) by presenting a new algorithm for mining API call patterns. It also uses machine learning techniques such as probabilistic modeling (LG) and information retrieval (IR) to improve the precision of the algorithm. Finally, it analyzes data from GitHub, which falls under the category of social and information networks (SI).
